title: VMWare throwing an error when launching gazebo

content.raw:
When attempting to run Gazebosim as installed by ros kinetic in Ubuntu 16.04 I get the following error:

This is using Gazebo7 and VMWare 12.1.1

```
#!bash

mroscoe@ubuntu:~$ gazebo
VMware: vmw_ioctl_command error Invalid argument.
```
